---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import FirstSteps from '../components/FirstSteps.astro';

const topics = [
	'Work stress and pressure to provide',
	'Anxiety and racing thoughts',
	'Depression and feeling numb',
	'Loneliness and isolation',
	'Anger that comes out sideways',
	'Feeling stuck, in life or in a relationship',
];
---

<Layout
	title="Men's Online Counseling in Colorado | Custom Counseling"
	description="Online therapy for men dealing with work stress, anxiety, depression, or feeling stuck. A counselor who gets how men talk. Colorado residents."
>
	<PageHero
		heading="Online Counseling for Men in Colorado"
		subhead="Stop bottling it up and get the help you need."
	/>

	<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 md:py-20">
		<div class="prose-site text-lg">
			<p>
				As <strong>men</strong>, we tend to bottle up our emotions. Maybe you were taught young to
				keep it to yourself. Maybe it feels like nobody really wants to hear it.
			</p>
			<p>
				So it builds. The stress from work comes home. The short fuse gets shorter. And the
				thoughts you have nowhere to unload keep circling at 2 a.m.
			</p>
			<p>
				Finding a therapist who actually gets how men think, and what we need, is
				hard. <strong>I get it, and I'm here to help.</strong>
			</p>
		</div>

		<h2 class="mt-12 text-3xl">What we can work on</h2>
		<ul class="mt-6 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
			{
				topics.map((topic) => (
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
						<span aria-hidden="true" class="h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-clay-400" />
						{topic}
					</li>
				))
			}
		</ul>

		<div class="prose-site mt-12 text-lg">
			<h2 class="text-3xl">No couch. No waiting room.</h2>
			<p>
				Sessions are online, so you can talk from your truck, your garage, or wherever you get
				privacy. It's a conversation, and it stays between us.
			</p>
			<p>
				There are no promises in therapy because it is not a miracle drug. However, I will do my
				best to help you where you are today.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<FirstSteps />
</Layout>
